{"id": 95, "name": "Texte de la commission sur la proposition de loi de M. Philippe Gosselin et plusieurs de ses coll\u00e8gues visant \u00e0 renforcer les conditions d'acc\u00e8s \u00e0 la nationalit\u00e9 fran\u00e7aise \u00e0 Mayotte (693)., n\u00b0\u00a0864-A0", "url": "/dyn/17/amendements/0864/AN/95", "date": "2025-02-03", "status": "Rejet\u00e9", "proposed_by": [{"first_name": "Davy", "last_name": "Rimane", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Soumya", "last_name": "Bourouaha", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "\u00c9douard", "last_name": "B\u00e9nard", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Jean-Victor", "last_name": "Castor", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Andr\u00e9", "last_name": "Chassaigne", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "\u00c9meline", "last_name": "K/Bidi", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Karine", "last_name": "Lebon", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Jean-Paul", "last_name": "Lecoq", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Fr\u00e9d\u00e9ric", "last_name": "Maillot", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Yannick", "last_name": "Monnet", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Marcellin", "last_name": "Nadeau", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "St\u00e9phane", "last_name": "Peu", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Mereana", "last_name": "Reid Arbelot", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Nicolas", "last_name": "Sansu", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Emmanuel", "last_name": "Tjibaou", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}], "summary": "Cet amendement vise \u00e0 mod\u00e9rer le durcissement de la condition d\u2019acquisition de la nationalit\u00e9 fran\u00e7aise au titre du droit du sol, port\u00e9 par la proposition de loi.Les difficult\u00e9s ind\u00e9niables que conna\u00eet Mayotte ne r\u00e9sument pas \u00e0 cette question. Le rapporteur de la proposition l\u2019a lui-m\u00eame reconnu sur Europe 1, en indiquant\u00a0: \u00ab\u00a0Personne ne pr\u00e9tend que cette proposition de loi permettra de r\u00e9soudre toutes les difficult\u00e9s de Mayotte. Ce n'est pas la r\u00e9ponse miracle au fait migratoire \u00e0 Mayotte\u00a0\u00bb.Compte tenu de l\u2019inefficacit\u00e9 d\u00e9j\u00e0 acquise de ce durcissement envisag\u00e9, il para\u00eet pertinent de le mod\u00e9rer."}